: ''Requires the Essentials plugin to activate.''

Earn a certain amount of money after starting quest.

== Options ==
{|
|-
! Key
! Description
! Type
! Required
! Default
! Notes
|-
| <code>amount</code>
| The amount to earn.
| Integer
| Yes
| -
| -
|}

== Examples ==
Earn $1000:

```yaml
essentialsbalance:
  type: "essentials_moneyearn"
  amount: 1000                          # amount of money to earn
```
